### Health Check
GET http://localhost:5000/api/health

### Get All Medicines
GET http://localhost:5000/api/medicines

### Search Medicines - Paracetamol
GET http://localhost:5000/api/medicines/search?q=paracetamol

### Search Medicines - Pain
GET http://localhost:5000/api/medicines/search?q=pain

### Autocomplete Suggestions
GET http://localhost:5000/api/medicines/suggest/autocomplete?q=para

### Get Medicine by ID
GET http://localhost:5000/api/medicines/paracetamol-500

### Get Similar Medicines
GET http://localhost:5000/api/medicines/paracetamol-500/similar

### Get Alternative Medicines
GET http://localhost:5000/api/medicines/paracetamol-500/alternatives

### Register User
POST http://localhost:5000/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "password123",
  "name": "Test User"
}

### Login User
POST http://localhost:5000/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### Get User Profile (requires token)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/users/profile
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE
